This file contains installation and/or configuration instructions.


* Required Software Packages:
> SH Shell (Any unix based system)
> Python 2.6 - http://python.org/
> Cheetah Template Engine - http://cheetahtemplate.org/


* Enabling PDF output
> To use PDF output you will need a new Firefox (3.0+) and the cli print extension.
> See: http://torisugari.googlepages.com/commandlineprint2

> Background images and background colors do not work with automated PDF generation.
> In such cases you will need to perform the PDF convertion manually.